oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (red, yellow and black on white) announcing Radio Week in celebration of 68 years of the Tennessee Association of Broadcasters. Event features Ruby Amanfu with Jeremy Fetzer at the CMA theater on September 20. Poster features a metal photoplate of Ruby Amanfu.
